1
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:35,940
=The Embroidered Truth=

2
00:00:47,159 --> 00:00:47,960
Your Highness,

3
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:50,280
I've found a new pattern.

4
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:51,759
It's bold and vibrant.

5
00:00:51,960 --> 00:00:53,240
It outshines all flowers.

6
00:00:54,119 --> 00:00:55,159
Master Wu,

7
00:00:55,719 --> 00:00:56,719
if you can

8
00:00:56,719 --> 00:00:59,079
make me as beautiful as I was
the year I met the Prince,

9
00:00:59,719 --> 00:01:02,560
I will grant you supreme
status in Jinxiu City.

10
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:06,959
No one will see you as just
an embroiderer.

11
00:01:10,519 --> 00:01:11,840
If you fail,

12
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:15,840
you'll be nothing more than
a dog at my feet.

13
00:01:21,719 --> 00:01:22,519
Women, until death,

14
00:01:22,519 --> 00:01:23,760
rely on men!

15
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:26,319
So why can't I let them
rely on me for a while?

16
00:01:29,359 --> 00:01:30,879
The Flower Festival.

17
00:01:32,599 --> 00:01:33,560
Lin Rulan.

18
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:37,840
I will fight you to the death.

19
00:01:38,580 --> 00:01:42,580
=Episode 23=

20
00:01:42,959 --> 00:01:43,760
Get out!

21
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:53,920
We've found other victims.

22
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,920
We just need you to testify.

23
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:57,560
Miss...

24
00:02:01,959 --> 00:02:02,760
Out, out!

25
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:03,760
(Ink Studio)
Get lost!

26
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:04,680
(Ink Studio)
Don't come back!

27
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:05,079
(Ink Studio)
Miss.

28
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:06,319
If you're willing to testify...

29
00:02:15,599 --> 00:02:16,759
You didn't leave.

30
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:24,120
The Flower Festival isn't here yet.

31
00:02:24,479 --> 00:02:25,560
How could I leave?

32
00:02:26,159 --> 00:02:27,000
Wu Lian told me

33
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:28,080
you were dead.

34
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,919
Dead, yet reborn.

35
00:02:31,319 --> 00:02:33,840
Your Highness, will you hear me out?

36
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,960
So my wife was bewitched by you?

37
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:39,199
I never bewitch anyone.

38
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:41,039
I only speak the truth.

39
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:42,560
That's it.

40
00:02:44,879 --> 00:02:45,960
In our dynasty,

41
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:47,080
justice relies on evidence.

42
00:02:47,719 --> 00:02:50,000
If you bring me evidence
before the Flower Festival,

43
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:50,800
bring me witnesses,

44
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:52,400
and I will see justice done.

45
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:54,039
If you cannot,

46
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:56,520
you will be guilty of
false accusation.

47
00:02:56,639 --> 00:02:57,439
Your Highness,

48
00:02:58,479 --> 00:03:00,039
I stake my life on this.

49
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:02,639
If I cannot find witnesses
by tomorrow,

50
00:03:02,759 --> 00:03:04,000
if I cannot produce evidence,

51
00:03:04,919 --> 00:03:06,280
I will die again

52
00:03:06,719 --> 00:03:07,759
to atone to the world

53
00:03:08,159 --> 00:03:09,360
and to thank you

54
00:03:09,599 --> 00:03:10,719
for hearing me out today.

55
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:35,240
You don't trust a word I say,

56
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:38,599
yet you believe the ravings
of a dead woman.

57
00:03:38,759 --> 00:03:40,199
We've been married for over
a decade.

58
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:41,800
It's not that I don't trust you.

59
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:45,159
It's that I know your temperament.

60
00:03:47,159 --> 00:03:48,319
If you truly know me,

61
00:03:50,319 --> 00:03:52,039
do you know that waiting
for you all three years

62
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:55,120
has worn me out?

63
00:03:58,599 --> 00:03:59,479
I appreciate it.

64
00:04:00,319 --> 00:04:01,240
But as a servant of the state,

65
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:02,240
fighting for my country,

66
00:04:02,919 --> 00:04:04,439
how can I be hindered by
family matters?

67
00:04:04,719 --> 00:04:05,840
Tomorrow at the Flower Festival,

68
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:07,800
we will pray for the people.

69
00:04:08,199 --> 00:04:09,319
You are unsettled today.

70
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:11,520
Go rest in your room.

71
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:25,279
Jasmine blooms,

72
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,639
fragrance wafts.

73
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:29,959
Xiaoshou.

74
00:04:31,319 --> 00:04:32,160
Don't be angry.

75
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,319
Don't be angry.

76
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:35,120
Don't be angry.

77
00:04:35,959 --> 00:04:36,759
Mr. Liu,

78
00:04:38,199 --> 00:04:39,040
Mr. Liu,

79
00:04:39,399 --> 00:04:40,199
any luck?

80
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:43,519
Still no embroider willing
to testify?

81
00:04:45,399 --> 00:04:46,920
No wonder Wu Lian keeps
getting away with it.

82
00:04:47,279 --> 00:04:48,680
These people have lost their minds

83
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:49,759
or tougues.

84
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:51,560
Either they won't speak,

85
00:04:51,759 --> 00:04:52,680
or they don't remember.

86
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:54,920
Most of these girls are
commoners' daughters.

87
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:57,519
They entered Yanyu Embroidery
House to learn a trade

88
00:04:57,519 --> 00:04:58,519
and marry well.

89
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:00,480
Now that we're bringing this up,

90
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:02,800
it's no wonder they won't testify.

91
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,560
Their husbands' families,

92
00:05:04,879 --> 00:05:07,120
who married these girls, also want

93
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,040
to gain favor

94
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:08,839
from the manor.

95
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,000
They did many awful things.

96
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:11,839
They don't dare oppose it.

97
00:05:12,319 --> 00:05:13,560
Having a daughter

98
00:05:13,879 --> 00:05:16,319
is just a bargaining chip
for parents and husbands.

99
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,480
Don't overthink it.

100
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:20,439
Jia Yi died at Wu Lian's hands.

101
00:05:20,519 --> 00:05:21,439
He deserved it.

102
00:05:23,399 --> 00:05:24,439
Heaven's will is clear.

103
00:05:24,959 --> 00:05:26,519
Retribution will come.

104
00:05:26,879 --> 00:05:27,879
No matter what,

105
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:30,160
tomorrow, when the Prince
and his wife ascend the wall,

106
00:05:30,399 --> 00:05:31,759
I must make my move.

107
00:05:33,759 --> 00:05:37,079
(The time has come to seek
justice for you three years ago.)

108
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:40,079
(For all the women who
suffered humiliation,)

109
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:42,240
(justice is at hand.)

110
00:05:42,860 --> 00:05:48,180
(Hongyun Gate)

111
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:58,079
Prince Jingyuan and the
Princess Consort

112
00:05:58,160 --> 00:06:00,639
(Hongyun Gate)
celebrate the Flower Festival with us.

113
00:06:02,839 --> 00:06:06,279
Long live the Prince!

114
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:09,480
(Hongyun Gate)
Long live the Princess Consort!

115
00:06:09,759 --> 00:06:10,560
Rise.

116
00:06:10,759 --> 00:06:12,160
Thank you, Your Highness.

117
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:38,800
I, Lin Rulan,

118
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:41,000
have a grievance.

119
00:06:42,319 --> 00:06:43,759
I, Lin Rulan,

120
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:45,680
have a grievance.

121
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:49,759
You let her leave

122
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:52,120
so she could do this today?

123
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,279
The people's voice matters.

124
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:54,720
If she speaks for the people,

125
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:55,680
why not?

126
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:58,920
Step forward.

127
00:07:02,279 --> 00:07:04,920
Master Wu, confess now.

128
00:07:06,079 --> 00:07:06,879
Magistrate Yu,

129
00:07:07,519 --> 00:07:09,439
I don't know what you mean.

130
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:19,839
Rulan's calm, courage, and vision today

131
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:21,839
are worlds apart from three years ago.

132
00:07:21,959 --> 00:07:23,319
My Lady, you taught her well.

133
00:07:23,759 --> 00:07:25,240
And Miss Rulan is diligent
and thoughtful.

134
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:27,680
These days in Jinxiu City,
she's like a different person.

135
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:30,199
She didn't waste my efforts.

136
00:07:30,959 --> 00:07:32,680
Today, let me see

137
00:07:32,959 --> 00:07:34,720
what filth my cousin

138
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:36,279
has been hiding

139
00:07:36,519 --> 00:07:38,279
up her sleeve.

140
00:07:38,300 --> 00:07:41,620
(Complainant: Lin Rulan
Defendant: Wu Lian)

141
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:47,160
I only ask for justice.

142
00:07:47,319 --> 00:07:49,759
Justice for the late Ms. Meng Wan.

143
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:52,759
Justice for the women
defiled by Wu Lian.

144
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:56,959
Justice for the Lin Rulan who died
beneath this wall three years ago.

145
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,040
Wu Lian,

146
00:07:58,879 --> 00:08:00,279
do you have anything to say?

147
00:08:00,959 --> 00:08:01,639
Your Highness,

148
00:08:02,439 --> 00:08:05,279
impersonating a Lady is
a capital offense.

149
00:08:06,319 --> 00:08:08,000
A woman of unknown identity,

150
00:08:08,199 --> 00:08:10,040
why should anyone believe her?

151
00:08:10,399 --> 00:08:12,240
It's true I impersonated Lady Cheng'en,

152
00:08:12,639 --> 00:08:14,079
but there were reasons.

153
00:08:14,279 --> 00:08:16,319
Since both the accuser and the
accused are guilty,

154
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:18,360
and the case is complex
and bizarre,

155
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,680
let's handle it elsewhere.

156
00:08:19,759 --> 00:08:20,879
Have Magistrate Yu judge it.

157
00:08:21,079 --> 00:08:23,199
Precisely because it's
complex and bizarre,

158
00:08:23,399 --> 00:08:24,920
I will judge it myself.

159
00:08:24,959 --> 00:08:27,600
This woman impersonated Ruoheng.
There must be a reason.

160
00:08:28,199 --> 00:08:29,680
After I ask my cousin...

161
00:08:29,879 --> 00:08:31,959
Is there any reason to wait, Wenyue?

162
00:08:32,279 --> 00:08:33,960
Today, I want to see

163
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,399
what this complex and bizarre case

164
00:08:35,759 --> 00:08:37,120
is all about.

165
00:08:37,519 --> 00:08:38,360
Your Highness.

166
00:08:39,519 --> 00:08:41,080
She is the real Ruoheng.

167
00:08:41,679 --> 00:08:42,639
Have you met?

168
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:43,879
Wenyue,

169
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:45,519
when the Prince returned to
the capital,

170
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:46,799
we had already met.

171
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:48,879
When discussing Jinxiu City,

172
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:53,159
he invited me to see the city's
beauty and customs.

173
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:58,840
I accuse Wu Lian, Master of
Yanyu Embroidery House.

174
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,720
Relying on the Princess Consort's power,

175
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:01,960
he bullies the weak,

176
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:03,159
does whatever he wants,

177
00:09:03,159 --> 00:09:04,480
defiles embroiderers,

178
00:09:04,679 --> 00:09:07,000
and murdered Ms. Meng Wan.

179
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:09,960
This woman first impersonated
Lady Cheng'en

180
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:11,039
to sneak into the manor.

181
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:12,240
Her Highness, in her kindness,

182
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:14,600
accepted her because of the jade
tablet proving Lady Cheng'en's identity.

183
00:09:14,799 --> 00:09:16,240
But she showed no gratitude.

184
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,720
She caused a scene at the
Flower Festival!

185
00:09:17,879 --> 00:09:21,279
Your Highness, this woman must
have ulterior motives,

186
00:09:21,519 --> 00:09:22,759
spreading discord!

187
00:09:22,759 --> 00:09:23,960
You're lying!

188
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,679
First, you defiled the embroiderers,

189
00:09:25,799 --> 00:09:26,799
then drove me to suicide,

190
00:09:26,919 --> 00:09:28,320
and killed Ms. Meng Wan!

191
00:09:28,559 --> 00:09:29,919
Truly deserving of your reputation.

192
00:09:30,159 --> 00:09:30,960
Wu Lian

193
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:33,039
certainly has a way with words.

194
00:09:33,559 --> 00:09:34,440
Lin Rulan,

195
00:09:34,559 --> 00:09:35,720
do you have evidence?

196
00:09:36,159 --> 00:09:36,960
Yes.

197
00:10:08,560 --> 00:10:11,520
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

198
00:10:11,760 --> 00:10:14,760
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

199
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:18,720
♪The past no longer binds♪

200
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:22,920
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

201
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:27,480
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

202
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:31,200
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

203
00:10:31,560 --> 00:10:33,560
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

204
00:10:33,560 --> 00:10:37,640
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

205
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:40,240
♪For your faith that never broke♪

206
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:44,560
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

207
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:47,360
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

208
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:51,600
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

209
00:10:52,800 --> 00:10:55,280
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

210
00:10:55,400 --> 00:10:58,040
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

211
00:10:58,040 --> 00:11:00,640
♪One thought turns into ash♪

212
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:06,960
♪No future left to write♪

213
00:11:08,040 --> 00:11:09,840
♪If I never fall♪

214
00:11:09,880 --> 00:11:12,240
♪How could this waiting end♪

215
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:13,600
♪If I bear no scars♪

216
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:15,920
♪How could I challenge fate♪

217
00:11:15,920 --> 00:11:18,280
♪I knew there was no way back♪

218
00:11:18,280 --> 00:11:22,280
♪Yet I left this hope behind♪

219
00:11:22,400 --> 00:11:24,520
♪For your faith that never broke♪

220
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:28,680
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

221
00:11:29,640 --> 00:11:31,560
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

222
00:11:31,560 --> 00:11:35,960
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

223
00:11:37,040 --> 00:11:39,640
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

224
00:11:39,680 --> 00:11:42,240
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

225
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:44,600
♪One thought turns into ash♪

226
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:50,960
♪No future left to write♪

227
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:54,240
♪The lamp is out, you're gone♪

228
00:11:55,520 --> 00:11:57,640
♪Heaven and earth fall silent♪

229
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:01,520
♪If we meet again someday♪

230
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:07,760
♪This longing sleeps beneath the snow♪
